2013-02-16  Werner LEMBERG  <wl@gnu.org>

	* doc/groff.texinfo: Improve documentation of `.substring'.

	Reported by Jim Avera <james_avera@yahoo.com>.

2013-02-13  Werner LEMBERG  <wl@gnu.org>

